  <section class="case-section" data-animate>
    <p class="case-section__label">// the result</p>
    <h2 class="case-section__title">The Result</h2>
    <p>For the first time, all of MIT's engineering academic offerings — more than 20 undergraduate majors and a full range of graduate programs — are presented in a single, coherent experience. The site serves students, supports institutional strategy, advances public understanding of engineering, and is built to last. A governance framework with assigned content owners and regular review cycles ensures it stays accurate, current, and mission-aligned.</p>
